    Towards a Science of Mind
    Jerome Feldman (ICSI and UC Berkeley)
    Comments: 13 pages and 1 Figure. The ancient mind/body remains a scientific and existential mystery. This article develops a methodology for an incremental Science of Mind and describes some ongoing successes
    Subjects: General Literature (cs.GL); Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI); Neurons and Cognition (q-bio.NC)
